Fake user feedbacks

Source: R/fake_products.R
fake_user_feedback.Rd

Fake user feedbacks

fake_user_feedback(
  n,
  seed = 2811,
  from = "2012-01-01 00:00:01",
  to = "2020-01-01 00:00:01"
)

Arguments

n

Number of feedbacks to generate
seed

the random seed, default is 2811
from

the date to cover
to

the date to cover

Value

a dataframe

Examples

fake_user_feedback(10)
